README for Siesta 0.63

=head1 NAME

Siesta - the Siesta mailing list manager.


=head1 DEPENDENCIES

This module has external dependencies on the following modules:

 Apache::Session::SharedMem
 Class::Accessor::Fast
 Class::DBI::BaseDSN
 Class::DBI::SQLite
 Digest::MD5
 Email::Folder
 Email::LocalDelivery	0.05
 Email::Simple	1.4
 File::Basename
 File::Find::Rule
 File::Path
 Mail::Address
 Mail::DeliveryStatus::BounceParser
 Module::Build	0.18
 Python::Serialise::Marshal
 Storable
 String::ShellQuote
 Sys::Hostname
 Template
 Test::More
 Tie::IxHash
 UNIVERSAL::require

=head1 INSTALLATION

 perl Build.PL
 perl Build test

and if all goes well

 perl Build install

=head1 HISTORY

What changed over the last 3 revisions

=over

=item 0.63	2003-08-09

	improvements to Siesta::UserGuide
	big bug in List->set_plugins fixed (thanks Jody)
	-f switch
	many many more


=item 0.62    2003-07-28

	fixed a syntax error in Siesta::Web (I be slack)


=item 0.61    2003-07-28

	Fix MANIFEST, ship Siesta::Build
	Have Siesta::Web point within Config('root')/web-frontend

=back

